            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Construction Sites: Equipment Serial Number Recovery</h3>

            <p class="mb-6">
              Construction companies can now capture serial numbers on stolen equipment, leading to recovery rates
              jumping from 21% to 67%. The clear footage also helps prosecute organized theft rings that previously
              operated with impunity.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Retail Parking Lots: Liability Protection</h3>

            <p class="mb-8">
              Shopping centers using FDC have successfully defended against 90% of slip-and-fall claims by providing
              indisputable video evidence. The frame-by-frame clarity shows exactly what happened, protecting
              businesses from fraudulent lawsuits.
            </p>

