            <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-300">S-VIDIA FDC Performance Metrics:</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Compression Efficiency:</strong> 60-70% better than H.264</li>
                <li><strong>Frame Independence:</strong> 100% (every frame is complete)</li>
                <li><strong>Motion Detection Accuracy:</strong> 95%+</li>
                <li><strong>Processing Latency:</strong> &lt;50ms</li>
                <li><strong>Evidence Recovery Rate:</strong> 94%</li>
                <li><strong>Court Admissibility:</strong> 100% acceptance rate</li>
                <li><strong>Storage Reduction:</strong> 60% less than traditional</li>
                <li><strong>CPU Usage:</strong> 40% lower than H.265</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Why Tacoma Businesses Are Switching to S-VIDIA</h2>

            <p class="mb-6">
              With Tacoma experiencing 5,901 vehicle thefts in 2023 and property crime rates 125% above the national
              average, businesses can't afford security systems that fail when needed most. S-VIDIA equipped businesses
              report:
            </p>

            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
              <li>92% reduction in successful thefts</li>
              <li>87% decrease in false alarms</li>
              <li>73% faster police response due to clear evidence</li>
