            <p class="mb-6">
              While competitors struggle to squeeze marginal improvements from 20-year-old compression technology,
              S-VIDIA continues advancing FDC capabilities. Coming developments include:
            </p>

            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
              <li>AI-powered predictive threat detection</li>
              <li>8K resolution support with no storage penalty</li>
              <li>Facial recognition integration</li>
              <li>Automated license plate alerts to law enforcement</li>
              <li>Blockchain evidence authentication</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Conclusion: Transform Your Security Infrastructure</h2>

            <p class="mb-6">
              Every day you operate with inferior security technology is another day you're vulnerable. The criminals
