              S-VIDIA's FDC technology represents a fundamental breakthrough in surveillance—purpose-built for evidence collection with unmatched quality, efficiency, and court admissibility. The question isn't whether you can afford to upgrade; it's whether you can afford not to.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Experience S-VIDIA Technology Firsthand</h3>
